                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="4r" to="18r" facs="004"/><title>Asmat Prayer of Saint John told to him by God, when he tended the tomb of Saint Mary, for Wealth and Against Enemies. interwoven with various Images, e.g., of Saint John, beginning: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለፅንሰትከ፡ ወለልደትከ፡ መአድም፡</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="19r" to="19v" facs="019"/><title>Asmat Prayer for Protection</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
